    <item>
      <title>1 ग्रहणम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/shrIvaiShNavaH/mADabhUShi-vIrarAghavaH/01_pUrva-prayoga-chandrikA/vangIpura-shrInivAsa-anukramaNikA/14_vedavratAni/06_vaishvadeva-vratam/1_grahaNam/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/shrIvaiShNavaH/mADabhUShi-vIrarAghavaH/01_pUrva-prayoga-chandrikA/vangIpura-shrInivAsa-anukramaNikA/14_vedavratAni/06_vaishvadeva-vratam/1_grahaNam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;तरपणनतम&#34;&gt;तर्पणान्तम्&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;आचार्यः प्राणानायम्य&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अमुक-गोत्रममुकशर्माणं माणवकं वैश्वदेवव्रतेन कर्मणा संस्करिष्यामि&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इति सङ्कल्प्य, &amp;ldquo;वैश्वदेवव्रतं चरिष्यामी&amp;quot;ति शिष्यं वाचयित्वा,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;उपवीतादिधारणं स्नानं&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/mantrAdi/vishvAn_devAn_kANDarShIn.md&#34; unfilled newLevelForH1=&#34;5&#34; includeTitle=&#34;false&#34;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;  &#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/mantrAdi/prajApatim_kANDarShim.md&#34; unfilled newLevelForH1=&#34;5&#34; includeTitle=&#34;false&#34;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;  &#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/mantrAdi/sAMhitI-yAjnikI-vAruNyAdi-tarpaNam.md&#34; unfilled newLevelForH1=&#34;5&#34; includeTitle=&#34;false&#34;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;  &#xA;&lt;p&gt;च तर्पयित्वा,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;हम&#34;&gt;होमः&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अग्नेरुपसमाधानाद्यग्निमुखान्ते शिष्येणान्वारब्धः,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/mantrAdi/vishvebhyo_devebhyaH_kANDarShibhyaH.md&#34; unfilled newLevelForH1=&#34;5&#34; includeTitle=&#34;false&#34;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;  &#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/brAhmaNam/sarva-prastutiH/2/8_kAmya-pashavaH/6_sAvitrAdi-pashu-sUktAni/02_vaishvadevam&#34; unfilled newLevelForH1=&#34;5&#34; includeTitle=&#34;false&#34;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(वि᳓श्वेभ्यो देवे᳓भ्य इदं᳓ न᳓ म᳓म । इति सर्वत्र त्यागः। )&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;साँहितीभ्यो, याज्ञिकीभ्यो वारुणीभ्यो ब्रह्मणे स्वयम्भुवे सदसस्पतये च हुत्वा,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/mantrAdi/sAMhitI-yAjnikI-vAruNI-brahma-sadasaspatayaH.md&#34; unfilled newLevelForH1=&#34;5&#34; includeTitle=&#34;false&#34;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;  &#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;वरत-चरषयम&#34;&gt;व्रतं चरिष्यामि&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(अधः &amp;ldquo;काण्डर्षि᳓भ्यो वैश्वदेव-व्रत᳓म्&amp;rdquo; इत्यूहनीयम्।)&#xA;+++(माणवकः अग्नेरुत्तरतः स्थित्वा -)+++&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;5&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/AraNyakam/sarva-prastutiH/07_pravargyAdi/84_agne_vratapate&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h5&gt;८४ अग्ने व्रतपते ...{Loading}...&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अग्ने॑ व्रतपते!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2 उत्सर्गः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/shrIvaiShNavaH/mADabhUShi-vIrarAghavaH/01_pUrva-prayoga-chandrikA/vangIpura-shrInivAsa-anukramaNikA/14_vedavratAni/06_vaishvadeva-vratam/2_utsargaH/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/gRhyam/paddhatiH/shrIvaiShNavaH/mADabhUShi-vIrarAghavaH/01_pUrva-prayoga-chandrikA/vangIpura-shrInivAsa-anukramaNikA/14_vedavratAni/06_vaishvadeva-vratam/2_utsargaH/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;आचार्यः प्राणानायम्य, अमुक-गोत्रममुकशर्माणं माणवकं वैश्वदेवव्रतोत्सर्जनेन कर्मणा संस्करिष्यामीति सङ्कल्प्य,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;[[99]]&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;वैश्वदेवव्रतोत्सर्जनं चरिष्यामीति शिष्यं वाचयित्वा, उपवीतादिधारणस्नानतर्पणादि पूर्ववत् कारयित्वा, अग्नेरुपसमाधानाग्निमुखान्ते शिष्येणान्वारब्धः,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;विश्वेभ्यो देवेभ्यः काण्डर्षिभ्यः स्वाहा विश्वेभ्यो देवेभ्यः काण्डर्षिभ्य इदम् ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;आनो विश्वे, शन्नो देवा, ये सवितुः, अग्ने याहि, द्यौः पितः पृथिवि, विश्वे देवाः शृणुत&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इति षड्भिः षडाहुतीः, सांहितीः याज्ञिकीः, वारुणीः ब्रह्माणं स्वयम्भुवं सदसस्पतिं च प्रधानाहुतीः हुत्वा,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अग्ने व्रतपते काण्डर्षिभ्यः वैश्वदेवव्रतमचारिषं तदशकं तन्मे राधि ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;वायो व्रतपते काण्डर्षिभ्यः वैश्वदेवव्रतमचारिषं तदशकं तन्मे राधि ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;आदित्य व्रतपते काण्डर्षिभ्यः वैश्वदेवव्रतमचारिषं तदशकं तन्मे राधि ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;व्रतानां व्रतपते काण्डर्षिभ्यः वैश्वदेवव्रतमचारिषं तदशकं तन्मे राधि ।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
